Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to LTJG Brock Wendel Yates
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system on state route 19 in the county of Wyoming to LTJG Brock Wendel Yates.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to LTJG Brock Wendel Yates
